WEBVTT

00:08.480 --> 00:10.760
What a great trick, Mr. Song.

00:11.440 --> 00:12.960
If something happens to Mr. Wu,

00:13.040 --> 00:15.360
the emperor will think that the Dou family

00:15.440 --> 00:18.120
hurt someone out of ambition
and political differences!

00:18.880 --> 00:22.400
I can be the witness
to what happened here today.

00:23.000 --> 00:24.800
Song Mo trespassed on the Dou Residence.

00:24.880 --> 00:27.920
He threatened the official with a knife
and stopped people from saving lives.

00:28.000 --> 00:32.040
Even if this matter comes before
His Majesty, this will be the truth.

00:36.240 --> 00:37.640
It's lively.

00:39.320 --> 00:40.760
Seems like

00:41.360 --> 00:43.600
you're doing a sword performance
to add to the fun.

00:44.760 --> 00:46.440
Old Madam Cui, good day.

00:47.640 --> 00:49.600
I just spent some time
to chat with my mother.

00:49.680 --> 00:50.760
What's going on?

00:50.840 --> 00:53.960
Dou Zhao refused to let anyone
send Mr. Wu to the physician.

00:54.040 --> 00:55.360
She wanted to treat Mr. Wu.

00:59.880 --> 01:00.800
Mr. Song.

01:02.120 --> 01:05.280
Cope with things slowly
and it will be satisfactorily resolved.

01:05.360 --> 01:07.760
The Duke of Ding is loyal.

01:07.840 --> 01:09.760
But you overstepped your authority
and searched the residence

01:09.840 --> 01:11.040
to silence your political opponents.

01:11.120 --> 01:14.680
You'll only harm your uncle
at this juncture.

01:15.280 --> 01:19.120
You've got to know
what's right and what's wrong.

01:19.200 --> 01:20.400
Old Madam Cui.

01:21.040 --> 01:24.040
Although I can't bring this to court,

01:24.120 --> 01:26.800
I've seen it clearly.

01:27.840 --> 01:32.760
I apologize for disturbing you.

01:34.760 --> 01:35.600
Step aside.

01:43.320 --> 01:45.600
Mr. Dai, you came from afar.

01:45.680 --> 01:47.720
I'm sorry for not
welcoming you at the door.

01:48.240 --> 01:52.240
If you could do me a favor,

01:52.760 --> 01:54.520
I'd be very grateful.

01:54.600 --> 01:57.000
Since you said so,

01:58.800 --> 02:02.120
I will not pursue what happened today.

02:02.200 --> 02:03.720
Step down.

02:06.440 --> 02:07.840
I made it!

02:07.920 --> 02:08.840
He's awake!

02:09.600 --> 02:10.440
De Zhen!

02:11.640 --> 02:13.800
The physician is here! Hurry up!

02:28.040 --> 02:30.920
Lung abscess will cause blood stasis.

02:31.000 --> 02:33.640
Luckily, you forced out the blood stasis.

02:33.720 --> 02:35.960
Otherwise, he might die.

02:46.800 --> 02:48.840
Old Madam, the young master is fine.

02:48.920 --> 02:51.640
I'm going to cook balloon flower
with ginseng for him now.

02:51.720 --> 02:52.840
Follow me.

03:03.000 --> 03:06.760
Thank you, Young Lady Zhao,
for saving my life.

03:07.360 --> 03:08.840
Mr. Wu, there's no need for this.

03:09.360 --> 03:10.560
We should be responsible too.

03:11.080 --> 03:13.160
We will prepare tonics and
deliver them to your residence.

03:13.240 --> 03:15.040
A lung abscess is a dangerous condition.

03:15.120 --> 03:16.640
You mustn't take it lightly.

03:16.720 --> 03:17.760
Take good care of yourself.

03:19.840 --> 03:22.720
De Zhen, it's true that she saved you.

03:22.800 --> 03:25.160
But this may not be an accident.

03:27.040 --> 03:30.200
Young Lady Zhao must know the truth.

03:31.480 --> 03:32.320
Yan Tang,

03:33.120 --> 03:34.320
look what you're saying.

03:35.240 --> 03:38.400
I got this when I went to help
with the disaster relief.

03:38.480 --> 03:40.240
I didn't even tell my grandfather.

03:40.320 --> 03:43.400
Moreover, no one knew the swallowtail
butterflies would cause a disturbance.

03:44.560 --> 03:46.880
Young Lady Zhao,
Yan Tang has agitated you.

03:46.960 --> 03:49.720
I apologize on his behalf.

03:57.440 --> 04:01.160
Young Lady Zhao, you disregarded
societal prejudices

04:01.240 --> 04:02.320
and saved my life.

04:02.400 --> 04:04.760
I couldn't have done more to repay you.

04:05.280 --> 04:08.080
-I can only…
-Mr. Wu, stop talking for now.

04:08.920 --> 04:10.120
Get well soon.

04:10.200 --> 04:12.080
We can't keep this from Old Mr. Wu.

04:12.160 --> 04:13.480
I'll take you back to the capital.

04:14.880 --> 04:15.760
Su Xin, Su Lan.

04:15.840 --> 04:18.360
-Lu Zheng, Lu Ming, go.
-Yes.

04:27.240 --> 04:28.640
Fortunately, Mr. Wu is fine.

04:29.360 --> 04:31.360
Mr. Song, you should be relieved.

04:31.880 --> 04:36.360
When Mr. Wu gets well,
the misunderstanding will be resolved.

04:37.200 --> 04:39.680
Quickly take Mr. Wu to
the guest room to take medicine.

04:42.880 --> 04:45.880
That's a very nice embroidery.

04:45.960 --> 04:48.400
Tell me. What is this?

04:50.000 --> 04:50.840
It's a tiger charm.

04:50.920 --> 04:52.200
Is it just a tiger charm?

04:53.200 --> 04:55.200
I ignored ethics and saved Mr. Wu.

04:55.840 --> 04:57.600
You should know that
I have nothing to hide.

05:18.520 --> 05:19.560
You're lying.

05:23.400 --> 05:25.000
You owe me an explanation.

06:57.200 --> 07:00.480
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL BLOSSOM
BY AUTHOR ZIZI FROM QIDIAN CHINESE WEBSITE

07:03.840 --> 07:04.840
CUI'S RESIDENCE

07:04.920 --> 07:06.000
Watch out for the steps.

07:06.880 --> 07:08.680
It's good that Mr. Wu is fine.

07:09.800 --> 07:12.960
Mr. Wu suffered from heat stroke.
He's fine now.

07:14.960 --> 07:16.840
-Stay here.
-Goodbye.

07:20.840 --> 07:22.440
Fortunately, nothing serious happened

07:23.040 --> 07:25.360
and the Wei family didn't see it.

07:25.960 --> 07:27.680
Zhao is really…

07:36.680 --> 07:39.800
Sister, I know that
Young Lady Zhao likes me.

07:41.080 --> 07:43.320
But she is unrefined.

07:44.760 --> 07:47.000
From now on, don't use
Chenxin Paper or Zijin Inkstone.

07:47.080 --> 07:48.720
Sell all your books.

07:48.800 --> 07:51.480
If you can do this,
we can call off the marriage.

07:53.760 --> 07:56.640
You can't bear it when I
talk about your precious stuff.

07:56.720 --> 07:59.200
Do you know how hard
it is for me to support the family now?

07:59.280 --> 08:02.400
You don't know this.
Her dowry is worth a lot!

08:02.480 --> 08:04.240
Wealth is not important.

08:04.320 --> 08:06.520
Marriage is about two people being happy.

08:06.600 --> 08:08.800
Right now, only she likes me.

08:08.880 --> 08:09.960
How can this be done?

08:11.400 --> 08:14.040
The first wife is for the family.

08:14.120 --> 08:17.160
If you want to marry someone whom
you love, you can take a concubine.

08:24.800 --> 08:26.440
But don't even think about
Young Lady Ming.

08:26.520 --> 08:28.360
Her maternal grandfather is Wang Xing Yi.

08:28.440 --> 08:30.000
You've seen how smart Wang Ying Xue is.

08:30.080 --> 08:33.320
Your title is prominent but false.

08:33.400 --> 08:34.720
You have no fame or official position.

08:36.679 --> 08:38.840
Fame and official positions are vulgar.

08:39.640 --> 08:41.559
It's fine not to seek fame and fortune.

08:43.360 --> 08:45.600
All right, all right. Whatever you decide.

08:46.200 --> 08:48.920
I'll treat it like marrying
a ball of cotton to plug my ears

08:49.000 --> 08:50.480
lest you nag at me every day.

08:53.160 --> 08:55.160
When I got this from Mr. Wu,

08:55.760 --> 08:57.840
it was filled with the fragrance
of a silk tree flower.

09:00.280 --> 09:01.520
Silk tree flower?

09:02.040 --> 09:05.120
As far as I know,
there are no silk tree flowers around.

09:05.880 --> 09:08.280
It's even less likely that there's
any pollen from them.

09:08.360 --> 09:09.560
That's right.

09:09.640 --> 09:11.040
I figured it out after consideration.

09:11.120 --> 09:14.240
You soaked the tiger charm in
the silk tree flower dew in advance.

09:14.320 --> 09:16.640
So it would retain
its aroma without pollen.

09:16.720 --> 09:18.360
The sun shone during the day.

09:18.440 --> 09:21.120
The borneol in the charm removed
the smell and diffused the fragrance.

09:21.640 --> 09:24.440
In less than two hours,
the smell was gone.

09:25.320 --> 09:27.440
Fortunately, Song Mo only
had a background in the military.

09:27.520 --> 09:29.240
He didn't know about
the tricks in this family.

09:29.840 --> 09:31.480
Otherwise, it would be a disaster for us!

09:32.000 --> 09:34.120
This is just baseless speculation.

09:34.200 --> 09:35.720
I advise you to be careful
with your words.

09:36.960 --> 09:40.280
Back then, you ate ephedra
but you framed me.

09:40.880 --> 09:43.480
And now, you've bewitched Mr. Wu

09:43.560 --> 09:45.880
by swapping the tiger charm
with Wei Ting Yu.

09:46.480 --> 09:48.880
Let me tell you, it is useless.

09:48.960 --> 09:50.760
You're destined to marry Wei Ting Yu.

09:50.840 --> 09:52.160
I'm not going to marry Wei Ting Yu.

09:52.240 --> 09:54.480
The parents will decide your marriage.

09:54.560 --> 09:55.600
It's not up to you.

09:56.200 --> 09:58.080
Wu Shan is my father's student.

09:58.160 --> 10:01.000
He is the good son-in-law
I selected for Ming.

10:01.080 --> 10:02.880
Don't even think about takng him.

10:02.960 --> 10:04.960
Mrs. Wei came today

10:05.040 --> 10:07.600
to discuss your marriage with Wei Ting Yu.

10:08.320 --> 10:10.440
If I don't make you marry
into the Wei family,

10:11.040 --> 10:14.040
as the mother, I'll feel guilty.

10:14.680 --> 10:16.320
You're very shrewd.

10:33.880 --> 10:35.000
Feeling better?

10:36.760 --> 10:38.600
Young Lady Zhao saved my life.

10:38.680 --> 10:39.720
You shouldn't doubt her.

10:40.320 --> 10:42.720
Did I say I doubted her?

10:43.320 --> 10:45.760
Had you not doubted her,
you wouldn't have made such a big fuss.

10:46.440 --> 10:48.440
Dou Shi Shu is ambitious

10:48.520 --> 10:50.160
while Dou Shi Ying
is uninterested in power.

10:50.240 --> 10:51.280
He is credulous.

10:51.880 --> 10:54.400
But Wang Ying Xue is pretentious
and has an evil heart.

10:54.480 --> 10:55.960
She is probably the cause of your illness.

10:56.760 --> 10:58.120
But from her reaction,

10:58.200 --> 10:59.840
she didn't want this disgraceful incident

10:59.920 --> 11:02.840
to happen to you and Young Lady Zhao.

11:02.920 --> 11:04.520
As for Young Lady Zhao…

11:05.360 --> 11:06.560
What about Young Lady Zhao?

11:07.440 --> 11:10.240
I can see that she is different
from the rest of the Dou family.

11:10.840 --> 11:13.200
I don't know why she hurt you by mistake.

11:14.080 --> 11:15.920
She was sincere in saving you
despite criticism.

11:16.520 --> 11:19.040
But she still chose
to cover up for the family.

11:19.880 --> 11:20.880
Do you mean that

11:21.400 --> 11:23.360
Young Lady Zhao also has feelings for me?

11:26.960 --> 11:28.320
If that's the case,

11:29.040 --> 11:29.880
it's my fortune.

11:30.480 --> 11:31.760
What I meant is

11:31.840 --> 11:34.120
the Dou family has a lot of tricks.

11:34.200 --> 11:36.400
A simple-minded person like you
can't handle it.

11:38.760 --> 11:40.640
How could I not know

11:41.160 --> 11:42.200
the filth in this wealthy family?

11:43.760 --> 11:45.680
But I'm different from you.

11:45.760 --> 11:47.520
You're experienced on the battlefield.

11:47.600 --> 11:48.920
Everyone looks like a bad guy to you.

11:51.240 --> 11:53.280
Young Lady Zhao is astute.

11:53.800 --> 11:55.000
She's a good match.

11:55.080 --> 11:57.240
You've got a thick head.

11:57.320 --> 11:58.360
You don't seem to get it.

12:00.040 --> 12:02.920
You sound like you know
Young Lady Zhao better than me.

12:03.000 --> 12:05.160
Could it be that
you secretly investigated her?

12:06.240 --> 12:07.400
I'll take that as a yes.

12:09.040 --> 12:11.080
Just now, you pulled me away
and didn't let me talk.

12:11.160 --> 12:12.360
I haven't…

12:14.520 --> 12:16.720
You're still coughing. You should
talk less with a lung abscess.

12:17.400 --> 12:20.120
I think Young Lady Zhao
doesn't have good skills.

12:20.200 --> 12:22.520
I'll get the imperial physician
to check on you later.

12:25.160 --> 12:27.840
DUKE OF YING'S RESIDENCE

12:32.560 --> 12:34.040
Sleeve length, one foot and eight inches.

12:37.880 --> 12:39.480
Shoulder width, one and a half feet.

12:41.160 --> 12:42.200
The shoulders are wider.

12:42.280 --> 12:44.120
I need to alter the cloak.

12:46.080 --> 12:47.400
Luckily, you stopped him.

12:47.480 --> 12:51.000
Otherwise, De Zhen would have gone
to ask for marriage to repay the favor.

12:52.720 --> 12:53.720
You may leave.

12:56.760 --> 12:58.320
The Dou family's trick is disgusting.

12:58.400 --> 13:01.240
Old Mr. Wu won't let De Zhen
do as he wishes for his marriage.

13:01.840 --> 13:03.960
We would rather offend
a gentleman than a villain.

13:04.040 --> 13:07.800
The Dou family,
especially Dou Shi Shu, is evil.

13:07.880 --> 13:09.040
He will definitely hurt someone.

13:10.720 --> 13:12.920
Fortunately, the Dou residence
is far from the estate.

13:13.000 --> 13:15.080
Madam Wang is also hostile to Dou Zhao.

13:15.840 --> 13:17.800
Dou Shi Shu is hypocritical
and greedy for power.

13:17.880 --> 13:19.320
Dou Zhao is smart and resourceful.

13:20.120 --> 13:21.040
If they're of the same mind,

13:21.800 --> 13:23.360
then we'll be in big trouble.

13:25.040 --> 13:27.280
I heard she had no parents
to protect her since she was a child.

13:27.800 --> 13:28.800
She must have had a difficult life.

13:30.000 --> 13:34.160
So it's normal for her to be sensitive,
thoughtful, alert, and resourceful.

13:35.720 --> 13:36.760
General Song!

13:39.000 --> 13:40.920
General Song,
General Yan sent a message saying

13:41.000 --> 13:43.320
that Dou Zhao has nothing
to do with the butterfly incident.

13:44.960 --> 13:45.800
I got it right.

13:49.200 --> 13:50.720
Although taking the waterway is slow,

13:51.720 --> 13:53.360
I expect my brother
will reach the capital soon.

13:56.240 --> 13:57.280
Mother.

13:57.800 --> 14:00.640
You have urinary issues and
you always feel dizzy and nauseous.

14:00.720 --> 14:02.480
Leave this needlework to the servants.

14:03.160 --> 14:04.680
Are you calling my needlework poor?

14:06.120 --> 14:07.200
Come here.

14:09.000 --> 14:11.200
It's been years
since I altered your clothes.

14:11.280 --> 14:13.800
I've made summer outfits
for your brother and you.

14:13.880 --> 14:16.080
You can wear them
when you return to Futing.

14:17.480 --> 14:18.640
Mother, Brother!

14:22.360 --> 14:24.040
Mrs. Song, Young Master Han
brought your medicine.

14:28.280 --> 14:30.320
Brother, you finally came home.

14:30.400 --> 14:32.640
But you only spent time with Mother.
You didn't talk to me.

14:34.920 --> 14:37.120
Mother said you like broiled venison.

14:37.200 --> 14:38.840
I plan to bring you a deer tomorrow.

14:39.440 --> 14:41.480
All right. If I can
have the venison you catch,

14:42.080 --> 14:45.120
I'll ask Father
to take you to Futing next year

14:45.640 --> 14:46.800
to join the military.

14:48.560 --> 14:49.840
It's a promise. Do not break it.

14:53.120 --> 14:55.040
You can arrange the prayer session now.

14:55.560 --> 14:57.040
We should inform our ancestors

14:57.120 --> 14:58.960
about Dou Zhao's marriage.

15:02.720 --> 15:04.400
Father, Uncle Shi Shu.

15:06.560 --> 15:08.240
I don't want to get married.

15:11.400 --> 15:12.440
Shou Gu.

15:13.480 --> 15:15.120
The current political situation
is unstable.

15:15.200 --> 15:16.920
This can be seen from what Song Mo did.

15:17.000 --> 15:19.680
I'm worried that I can't protect you.

15:20.280 --> 15:22.560
You're strong,
but you're a woman after all.

15:22.640 --> 15:24.080
If anything happens to the family,

15:24.160 --> 15:27.040
at least you have a husband
who can protect you.

15:27.120 --> 15:28.560
I don't need anyone's protection!

15:29.640 --> 15:32.640
All these years, I've studied hard,

15:32.720 --> 15:34.000
bought property, and made money

15:34.520 --> 15:37.240
because I don't want to rely on anyone.

15:37.320 --> 15:38.960
I can protect myself.

15:39.040 --> 15:42.160
Do you think money can buy you
permanent stability?

15:42.760 --> 15:43.760
I told you before.

15:44.560 --> 15:45.720
If a woman delays
her marriage for too long,

15:45.800 --> 15:48.360
she will definitely come up
with some deviant thoughts.

15:48.440 --> 15:49.960
Had I known this,

15:50.040 --> 15:52.160
I would have tied her to the bridal sedan.

15:52.240 --> 15:54.960
Even if you tie me up,
I will never marry Wei Ting Yu!

15:55.480 --> 15:56.880
-Shou Gu…
-Darn you!

15:56.960 --> 16:00.640
We haven't had a chance to talk
to you about the things you've done.

16:00.720 --> 16:02.280
You ignored your reputation.
Have you considered our family's?

16:02.360 --> 16:03.680
Shi Shu, what are you doing?

16:03.760 --> 16:06.280
Let's talk this over. Why did you hit her?

16:06.800 --> 16:08.080
Shou Gu.

16:09.640 --> 16:10.760
It's been so many years.

16:11.600 --> 16:13.600
You haven't changed at all, Father.

16:15.120 --> 16:17.240
I am your daughter.

16:18.640 --> 16:20.640
Why does Uncle Shi Shu have
the final say in my marriage?

16:21.240 --> 16:22.320
You scoundrel. Get out of my way.

16:22.400 --> 16:23.280
-Shi Shu!
-Don't stop me!

16:23.360 --> 16:24.240
-Shi Shu, stop hitting her.
-Get out of my way!

16:24.320 --> 16:25.520
-Shi Shu!
-Enough!

16:27.160 --> 16:28.320
-Mother.
-Mother.

16:28.400 --> 16:29.360
Get up.

16:32.360 --> 16:33.200
Are you all right?

16:37.160 --> 16:40.800
Marriage is a matter of
joy and sorrow in Shou Gu's life.

16:41.320 --> 16:43.120
How could you decide just like that?

16:43.960 --> 16:46.480
Do you treat her
like an item in a pawn shop?

16:47.000 --> 16:49.240
What kind of person is Wei Ting Yu?

16:49.320 --> 16:51.960
He frequents the brothel and
has a lot of women in his residence.

16:52.040 --> 16:54.280
He will definitely lose
his fortune sooner or later.

16:55.080 --> 16:58.320
Whoever arranged for this marriage
should go and cancel it.

16:58.400 --> 17:00.920
Mother, neither Shi Shu nor I wanted this.

17:01.720 --> 17:02.600
So what if we wanted that?

17:02.680 --> 17:05.720
Mother, I am now
the head of the Dou family.

17:06.240 --> 17:07.079
An unmarried daughter should
follow what her father says.

17:07.160 --> 17:09.440
It is fundamental that
the wife should follow the husband.

17:09.520 --> 17:11.319
Women are born to bear children,

17:11.400 --> 17:12.240
care for their husbands,
and raise the children.

17:12.319 --> 17:14.119
People say that

17:14.200 --> 17:15.040
a father is the guide for his son.

17:15.119 --> 17:17.640
If the father is unkind,
the son will leave him.

17:17.720 --> 17:19.240
A husband is the guide for his wife.

17:19.319 --> 17:21.480
If the husband isn't kind,
the wife can remarry.

17:21.560 --> 17:22.560
No one has ever said that

17:22.640 --> 17:24.800
women should be forced to obey.

17:24.880 --> 17:25.760
You…

17:26.280 --> 17:28.680
Grandma, don't get mad.

17:28.760 --> 17:29.640
Let's go.

17:33.120 --> 17:35.800
Mother, you were at odds with father,

17:35.880 --> 17:37.320
so you were lonely and resentful.

17:37.400 --> 17:40.440
Is that why you raised Dou Zhao
to harm the family?

17:46.880 --> 17:48.480
The fire is burning.

17:49.000 --> 17:50.600
All it needs is the hot oil.

17:55.040 --> 17:56.480
What did you say?

17:56.560 --> 17:59.200
-Shi Shu, please stop talking.
-Mother-in-law.

17:59.280 --> 18:00.200
Mother-in-law.

18:00.280 --> 18:01.720
Don't get them wrong.

18:01.800 --> 18:04.360
Shi Ying did that for the family.

18:04.440 --> 18:06.800
When you distributed food
for disaster relief,

18:06.880 --> 18:08.120
Shi Ying went to the imperial court

18:08.200 --> 18:10.000
and requested
a commendation order for you.

18:10.080 --> 18:12.440
He wanted to present it to you
at the family dinner

18:12.520 --> 18:14.040
to show his filial piety.

18:16.840 --> 18:21.640
COMMENDATION ORDER

18:24.720 --> 18:26.640
You went to get the award

18:27.800 --> 18:29.160
just to coax me

18:29.240 --> 18:31.120
into letting Shou Gu
getting married, right?

18:32.960 --> 18:34.160
Yet I thought

18:35.520 --> 18:37.680
you cared about me.

18:38.200 --> 18:39.520
Mother.

18:39.600 --> 18:41.360
I've missed you, really.

18:41.440 --> 18:43.240
I didn't intend to coax you.

18:43.320 --> 18:44.240
That's right.

18:44.320 --> 18:46.600
Shi Ying really wanted to
take you and Zhao home

18:46.680 --> 18:48.760
to enjoy family happiness.

18:49.280 --> 18:51.000
Do you think that by coming here,

18:51.080 --> 18:52.760
Dou Zhao is at your mercy?

18:54.200 --> 18:55.320
Listen.

18:55.920 --> 18:58.040
As long as I am still alive,

18:58.120 --> 19:00.040
Shou Gu will live with me at the estate.

19:00.120 --> 19:02.120
If the Wei family dares to
come and propose a marriage,

19:02.200 --> 19:05.160
I'll see if they can get through
the door of the estate.

19:07.200 --> 19:08.320
Mother!

19:09.920 --> 19:11.160
Mother-in-law!

19:12.360 --> 19:13.800
-Mother!
-I didn't mean that.

19:14.480 --> 19:16.160
She's ignorant.

19:16.240 --> 19:17.960
This is pissing me off.

19:18.040 --> 19:19.200
Mother-in-law!

19:19.720 --> 19:21.000
Shi Ying and I didn't mean that.

19:21.080 --> 19:23.440
Mother-in-law, don't take it to heart.

19:24.560 --> 19:27.120
Don't let it affect your health.

19:36.560 --> 19:37.920
You killed my mother back then.

19:38.440 --> 19:40.280
You took my family away
and you even hurt me.

19:40.360 --> 19:42.000
I didn't argue with you.

19:42.680 --> 19:44.320
Since I have returned to the estate,

19:44.840 --> 19:46.600
I have never fought with you.

19:46.680 --> 19:48.360
As long as you don't get married,

19:48.440 --> 19:51.520
as your father's wife, I will be uneasy.

19:52.120 --> 19:54.200
My grandmother is
the most important person to me.

19:54.720 --> 19:56.480
If you dare to set me up again

19:57.000 --> 19:58.520
and make her sad,

19:59.040 --> 20:00.800
you're going to get it from me.

20:02.200 --> 20:03.800
Shou Gu, come here!

20:04.480 --> 20:06.000
Don't waste your time with her!

20:17.280 --> 20:18.560
Does it hurt?

20:20.520 --> 20:22.280
It doesn't hurt anymore when you touch it.

20:23.640 --> 20:26.680
I forgot to hit him back for you.

20:28.640 --> 20:30.080
He talks about ethics and benevolence,

20:30.680 --> 20:32.360
but he does bad things.

20:32.960 --> 20:35.840
How like his animal of a father, Dou Duo.

20:37.720 --> 20:39.800
Grandma, you never
wanted to talk about Grandpa.

20:40.480 --> 20:42.720
What really happened back then?

20:44.480 --> 20:46.800
I won't let you follow the path
I went through.

20:47.840 --> 20:49.280
Dou Duo and I

20:49.800 --> 20:52.960
are the best example of a bad marriage
based on parental orders.

20:55.640 --> 20:59.240
The marriage ruined my life.

21:00.520 --> 21:02.840
It also ruined Tuo Niang's life.

21:03.360 --> 21:04.440
Tuo Niang?

21:06.320 --> 21:08.920
Isn't Tuo Niang my mom's personal maid?

21:09.000 --> 21:10.320
Why did you say you hurt her?

21:10.920 --> 21:13.800
Tuo Niang was the maid I brought
from my family.

21:14.560 --> 21:16.440
Dou Duo was lewd and lustful.

21:17.040 --> 21:19.200
Not only did he have concubines,

21:19.960 --> 21:22.960
he didn't even spare
the family members and servants.

21:24.120 --> 21:26.840
I took care of a lot of his messes.

21:27.640 --> 21:29.000
I didn't expect that

21:29.960 --> 21:33.800
he even hurt Tuo Niang,
who was already engaged.

21:34.560 --> 21:37.000
I knocked Dou Duo out with a bottle

21:37.080 --> 21:38.760
and saved Tuo Niang.

21:39.840 --> 21:41.600
In the Dou family,

21:41.680 --> 21:44.760
no one reprimanded Dou Duo
for his lewdness and violence.

21:44.840 --> 21:47.640
But they scolded me
for hurting my husband.

21:48.400 --> 21:50.240
They said I committed the seven offenses
and deserved a divorce.

21:51.560 --> 21:53.760
But they didn't dare to offend
the prominent Cui family.

21:54.560 --> 21:56.520
That's why they sent me to the estate

21:57.040 --> 21:58.800
and regarded me as an abandoned wife.

22:05.000 --> 22:06.640
You seriously injured Father.

22:06.720 --> 22:08.320
You've disgraced the family!

22:08.400 --> 22:09.240
You're unethical and immoral.

22:09.320 --> 22:12.120
It's all right not to have
a vicious mother like you!

22:12.200 --> 22:13.400
Leave now!

22:13.480 --> 22:14.320
Close the door!

22:17.320 --> 22:20.480
I didn't care about
what they said and did.

22:21.560 --> 22:23.040
But my real son

22:23.880 --> 22:26.040
avoided me like
I was a snake or a scorpion.

22:27.320 --> 22:29.600
He accused me of
being unworthy of being a mother.

22:32.400 --> 22:35.240
No wonder you've never wanted to
take the surname "Dou".

22:35.760 --> 22:37.240
You have been avoiding Dou's Residence.

22:39.720 --> 22:41.800
This is not a family.

22:41.880 --> 22:43.720
They don't deserve to be a family.

22:44.240 --> 22:45.720
So Grandma,

22:46.240 --> 22:48.040
it's not worth feeling sad for them.

22:48.560 --> 22:49.960
Let's forget about this family.

22:50.560 --> 22:51.920
We'll be together

22:52.000 --> 22:54.320
with Zhang Ru and An Su.

22:54.400 --> 22:56.000
The estate is our real home.

22:57.960 --> 22:59.640
You're good with words.

22:59.720 --> 23:00.760
You know how to make me feel good.

23:30.040 --> 23:31.280
Look at me!

23:33.240 --> 23:34.440
You got it on my face!

23:42.640 --> 23:44.400
I'm sorry to make an unexpected visit.

23:45.440 --> 23:48.640
-I'm sorry.
-It's all right.

23:51.040 --> 23:52.760
-Su Su, let's go.
-Let's go.

23:55.080 --> 23:55.960
Zhang Ru!

24:00.720 --> 24:02.640
Do you want to stay here for dinner?

24:02.720 --> 24:05.040
I'll cook a chicken for you. Let's go.

24:05.120 --> 24:06.280
Let's go.

24:08.000 --> 24:10.680
I'd better go to
the house and wait for you.

24:11.720 --> 24:12.840
It's all right.

24:14.360 --> 24:16.520
You must have something urgent
since you came all the way here.

24:17.280 --> 24:18.400
You can just tell me.

24:19.000 --> 24:20.040
I don't mind.

24:24.480 --> 24:26.560
-Leave.
-Yes.

24:36.200 --> 24:37.160
I thought

24:37.240 --> 24:39.320
you would follow your father
and move to the capital.

24:40.080 --> 24:42.440
But when I went to Dou's Residence,
I didn't see you.

24:42.520 --> 24:43.520
I…

24:44.040 --> 24:46.800
So I rushed over.

24:50.720 --> 24:53.040
During the Dragon Boat Festival,
to save me, you…

24:54.520 --> 24:55.680
Took off…

24:57.440 --> 24:58.800
You took off my clothes.

24:59.320 --> 25:01.520
There is no gender distinction
when saving someone.

25:02.320 --> 25:05.920
I would do the same for
the sick old farmer at the estate.

25:06.720 --> 25:07.960
Mr. Wu, don't take it to heart.

25:09.080 --> 25:10.640
You're easygoing and open-minded.

25:10.720 --> 25:11.840
But as a man,

25:11.920 --> 25:13.960
I can't sit back and see
your reputation damaged.

25:14.040 --> 25:15.400
I should be responsible.

25:18.560 --> 25:19.720
I am also willing to do so.

25:20.840 --> 25:21.880
I will tell the Wei family
to cancel the engagement

25:22.480 --> 25:24.400
and ask the matchmaker to
perform the formal proposal

25:25.160 --> 25:26.400
to marry you.

25:31.680 --> 25:32.680
Mr. Wu.

25:34.000 --> 25:36.520
You and I have only
met three times before.

25:37.040 --> 25:39.120
How can you base your marriage decision

25:39.200 --> 25:40.320
on these three occasions?

25:41.320 --> 25:42.480
You treat me well,

25:42.560 --> 25:44.400
so I will also tell you the truth.

25:45.040 --> 25:46.320
Whether it's Wei Ting Yu or you,

25:46.920 --> 25:48.200
I won't marry.

25:51.920 --> 25:54.640
It's triple.
So the total is nine taels of silver.

25:55.160 --> 25:56.400
Give it to me.

25:58.000 --> 25:59.840
He really came
to ask for a hand in marriage.

25:59.920 --> 26:04.160
Why isn't there a Wu
who wants to be responsible for me?

26:04.240 --> 26:06.000
All right, all right.
I'll be responsible for you.

26:07.480 --> 26:08.600
Let's go.

26:11.000 --> 26:12.920
I'm fascinated by your temperament.

26:14.040 --> 26:15.160
I miss you all the time.

26:16.360 --> 26:17.480
I thought

26:18.960 --> 26:20.200
we have a good rapport.

26:22.200 --> 26:25.040
Besides, you and I don't
have the same family backgrounds.

26:26.080 --> 26:27.800
I don't care about family background!

26:27.880 --> 26:28.960
Family background
cannot change one's wishes,

26:29.840 --> 26:31.640
but it can trap a person's lifestyle.

26:32.400 --> 26:33.640
Li Yi Shan once said that

26:34.280 --> 26:37.080
washing one's feet in the spring
and sipping tea while admiring flowers

26:37.680 --> 26:39.800
are indecent actions
that ruin the scenery.

26:40.400 --> 26:41.680
But I do that every day.

26:42.320 --> 26:43.480
I feel happy and comfortable.

26:44.440 --> 26:45.800
But this kind of happiness

26:46.400 --> 26:48.440
is not allowed by
those prestigious families.

26:50.080 --> 26:51.800
I understand. I really do.

27:05.640 --> 27:06.920
I haven't had it before,

27:07.840 --> 27:09.240
so I yearn for it even more.

27:12.800 --> 27:14.720
The infinite glory
of the prestigious families

27:15.440 --> 27:17.720
is a prison for me.

27:18.760 --> 27:21.800
Love, marriage, and fame

27:22.320 --> 27:23.280
are burdens.

27:24.400 --> 27:25.640
I don't want to be a virtuous woman.

27:26.960 --> 27:30.440
I only wish to sit in the breeze,

27:30.520 --> 27:31.840
hold the wine

27:32.440 --> 27:33.400
and enjoy it.

27:35.240 --> 27:36.240
I understand.

27:37.920 --> 27:39.720
Since I love your temperament,

27:39.800 --> 27:41.120
I will try my best to protect you.

27:41.200 --> 27:42.840
I will never let those shackles hurt you.

27:43.600 --> 27:44.960
I know

27:46.080 --> 27:47.480
how you feel.

27:48.080 --> 27:51.600
But your grandfather transferred you to
be the officer of the Ministry of Rites.

27:52.120 --> 27:53.600
Did he advise you about this?

27:58.200 --> 28:00.440
You can't even take care of yourself.

28:00.520 --> 28:02.760
How can you think about protecting others?

28:05.040 --> 28:07.480
I hope that you will
always be in good health

28:07.560 --> 28:08.760
and have a prosperous career.

28:09.480 --> 28:10.680
We probably won't meet again.

28:17.520 --> 28:18.720
Young Lady Zhao!

28:27.040 --> 28:29.680
I made this myself.

28:30.640 --> 28:31.880
It's not just a thank-you gift.

28:33.440 --> 28:34.920
It's also my reply.

28:35.760 --> 28:37.040
Please accept it.

28:41.760 --> 28:43.880
"We'll share a mutual sensibility

28:43.960 --> 28:46.160
and love together."

28:46.240 --> 28:49.520
"I dare to prove my sincerity."

28:52.600 --> 28:54.360
I'm not good at writing or reciting poems.

28:54.440 --> 28:56.920
But this is one tough guy.

29:01.000 --> 29:02.280
That's a good couplet.

29:03.360 --> 29:04.560
Unfortunately,
it was for the wrong person.

29:05.880 --> 29:06.720
Shou Gu,

29:07.320 --> 29:09.400
aren't you even a little moved?

29:10.280 --> 29:12.680
Love is about what we want.

29:12.760 --> 29:14.600
Stop making Zhao sad.

29:16.880 --> 29:19.960
A woman will never get away
with it once her heart is tempted.

29:20.840 --> 29:22.240
The price of temptation

29:23.480 --> 29:24.320
is too great.

29:24.920 --> 29:27.440
I noticed before that his hands
were thick with calluses.

29:27.520 --> 29:28.960
He must be very good at woodcrafting.

29:29.040 --> 29:32.840
But he never mentions
a word about this in front of outsiders.

29:33.440 --> 29:35.360
Woodcrafting is a humble task.

29:36.000 --> 29:37.360
Even though he likes it,

29:38.040 --> 29:39.480
he has to hide it.

29:41.040 --> 29:42.000
My ladies!

29:42.080 --> 29:43.520
Young Lady Ming
sent someone from the capital

29:43.600 --> 29:45.240
to deliver homemade glutinous rice balls.

29:50.160 --> 29:51.440
There are fillings with meat…

29:51.960 --> 29:53.600
Sesame paste…

29:54.200 --> 29:56.200
and sweetened bean paste.
She's attentive.

29:59.640 --> 30:02.360
"On the eve of the 15th,
the moon shines brightly."

30:02.440 --> 30:04.200
"I miss Grandma and Zhao very much."

30:04.280 --> 30:05.880
"That's why I made glutinous
rice balls and sent them over."

30:05.960 --> 30:07.440
"I hope you enjoy them."

30:08.200 --> 30:10.400
"Although it's not the Lantern Festival,

30:10.480 --> 30:13.720
I wish people could reunite
with their loved ones."

30:13.800 --> 30:17.160
"I hope you can come to the capital soon
and the family will reunite."

30:18.160 --> 30:19.640
"From Ming."

30:20.280 --> 30:22.120
Wang Ying Xue doesn't want you
to return to the capital.

30:22.200 --> 30:24.480
But she's not of the same mind
as her mother.

30:24.560 --> 30:25.720
She hopes you will return.

30:25.800 --> 30:27.080
I wonder if it's real.

30:29.880 --> 30:31.240
After experiencing all these things

30:31.760 --> 30:34.600
rejecting marriage with Wei Ting Yu,
and meeting Wu Shan,

30:35.120 --> 30:36.920
Wang Ying Xue was getting harsher.

30:37.680 --> 30:41.240
But Dou Ming is not
as hypocritical as I thought.

30:43.040 --> 30:44.320
Whatever it is,

30:44.400 --> 30:46.480
Zhao's only home is here

30:46.560 --> 30:48.560
We're her family, right?

30:49.400 --> 30:50.440
That's right.

30:55.000 --> 30:56.680
The Marquis of Jining has returned a gift.

30:56.760 --> 30:59.240
He sent brushes and inkstones
to Seventh Master and Fifth Master.

30:59.320 --> 31:00.840
He knows you love
calligraphy and painting,

31:00.920 --> 31:02.360
so he sent this Yuban Xuan paper.

31:02.960 --> 31:06.440
This paper is harder than the usual ones.

31:07.400 --> 31:08.680
It's not made of sandalwood bark.

31:13.560 --> 31:15.080
It's the bark of silkworm thorn.

31:15.720 --> 31:17.560
If this branch grows on a tree,

31:17.640 --> 31:19.400
it can protect someone from wind and rain.

31:19.480 --> 31:22.000
The fruits can satisfy one's hunger.

31:23.240 --> 31:25.360
The bark of silkworm thorn
can also be made into paper.

31:26.760 --> 31:28.920
They have different usages.

31:29.440 --> 31:30.800
How can you compare them?

31:31.640 --> 31:33.040
The same is true for humans.

31:33.640 --> 31:35.200
What's wrong with
the bark of silkworm thorn?

31:38.840 --> 31:39.840
Nothing.

31:40.800 --> 31:42.240
My father loves to write books.

31:42.320 --> 31:43.760
He uses a lot of paper.

31:43.840 --> 31:45.560
Send them to my father.

31:46.080 --> 31:47.200
All right.

31:56.640 --> 31:58.440
-Hurry up!
-All right.

31:58.520 --> 32:01.160
Remember everything I told you.

32:01.240 --> 32:02.960
-Yes.
-Mr. Wu.

32:03.040 --> 32:05.520
-Mr. Wu.
-Mr. Dou?

32:06.240 --> 32:09.280
For the past two days, the Office
of Transmission and the Six Ministries

32:09.360 --> 32:11.160
refuted my memorials.

32:11.240 --> 32:14.200
I had no choice but to send them here.

32:15.400 --> 32:18.080
The Grand Secretariat is virtuous.

32:20.280 --> 32:23.560
Mr. Dou, don't bother.

32:35.920 --> 32:38.680
MEMORIALS

32:44.920 --> 32:47.360
For Ying Xue and Shi Ying's sake,

32:47.960 --> 32:49.600
I have a message for you.

32:50.640 --> 32:53.560
"There is no path in the world
more treacherous than greed.

32:54.080 --> 32:56.320
Many people have misplaced
their lives because of it."

33:18.600 --> 33:23.440
ADMIRING THE LOFTY MOUNTAINS

33:33.000 --> 33:34.000
Mother.

33:35.760 --> 33:36.760
Yan Tang.

33:37.680 --> 33:39.360
Uncle's boat will arrive today.

33:39.440 --> 33:40.680
Gu Yu and I will go and pick him up.

33:43.600 --> 33:45.320
You're going to pick up your uncle.

33:46.320 --> 33:49.000
You can't disgrace the Jiangs.

33:49.080 --> 33:50.360
Rest assured.

33:50.440 --> 33:52.240
I've taken care of everything
in the court.

33:52.320 --> 33:53.600
I promise Uncle Mei Sun will be fine.

33:54.200 --> 33:57.440
Maybe after meeting
His Majesty during the day,

33:57.520 --> 33:58.840
we can reunite in the evening.

33:59.440 --> 34:00.960
The impeachment memorials

34:01.480 --> 34:03.600
were handed over.

34:04.440 --> 34:06.920
It's a good thing to have
His Majesty and your uncle

34:07.000 --> 34:08.840
meet and catch up on old times

34:09.360 --> 34:10.440
at this time.

34:13.199 --> 34:14.840
The Dou family did that.

34:14.920 --> 34:16.719
How could you still believe
what Young Lady Zhao said

34:17.679 --> 34:19.880
and prepare to present it to His Majesty?

34:19.960 --> 34:21.520
Everyone is in the game.

34:22.239 --> 34:24.360
Even if she treats me as a pawn,

34:24.440 --> 34:26.040
I can still be in control.

34:26.760 --> 34:28.600
Anyway, I know what to tell His Majesty.

34:28.679 --> 34:30.480
It's damp in the boat.

34:30.560 --> 34:31.800
I must change my uncle's dressing first.

34:36.040 --> 34:38.440
Gu Yu, isn't that the sedan chair
used to pick up my uncle?

34:43.360 --> 34:44.280
Stop.

34:50.239 --> 34:51.080
It's empty!

34:53.080 --> 34:54.120
Where's he?

35:04.840 --> 35:06.080
Get out of the way.

35:07.880 --> 35:09.080
Get out of the way.

35:11.640 --> 35:13.880
-Sir, you can't come in.
-How dare you stop me?

35:13.960 --> 35:14.960
Get out of the way!

35:17.160 --> 35:19.160
-Get out of the way!
-Sir, you can't come in!

35:19.240 --> 35:20.520
-You can't come in!
-Stop it!

35:20.600 --> 35:22.480
-Mr. Gu.
-Mr. Gu.

35:22.560 --> 35:23.400
WANG YUAN

35:23.480 --> 35:25.240
We're working on a case.
Please don't obstruct the investigation.

35:25.320 --> 35:26.520
Mr. Dai.

35:27.480 --> 35:28.560
Eunuch Wang.

35:28.640 --> 35:30.080
Why are you two here?

35:30.160 --> 35:32.240
We have duties here.

35:33.200 --> 35:34.320
Who is it over there? I'll go take a look.

35:35.360 --> 35:37.480
Mr. Gu. You can't go.

35:37.560 --> 35:38.480
I want to see it.

35:39.440 --> 35:40.280
-Mr. Gu!
-Get out of the way!

35:40.360 --> 35:41.600
-No!
-Get out of the way!

35:41.680 --> 35:42.720
Mr. Gu!

36:46.400 --> 36:48.600
Uncle! Wake up, Uncle!

36:50.960 --> 36:51.840
Uncle.

36:52.360 --> 36:53.920
Uncle, wake up. Uncle.

36:54.440 --> 36:56.200
Uncle!

37:02.920 --> 37:05.360
Why?

37:07.200 --> 37:08.840
How dare you disrupt the investigation?

37:08.920 --> 37:10.000
Are you seeking death?

37:12.280 --> 37:13.680
Get out of here!

37:13.760 --> 37:14.880
General Song!

37:16.000 --> 37:17.120
General Song.

37:17.840 --> 37:19.960
The Jiying Guards
serve under the emperor's orders.

37:20.040 --> 37:22.160
Anyone who interferes is like a traitor.

37:22.760 --> 37:25.240
Please disembark with Mr. Gu.

37:25.320 --> 37:28.760
The emperor's order is for you to safely
send the Duke of Ding to the capital

37:28.840 --> 37:30.640
or bring his body home?

37:31.240 --> 37:34.600
General Song, never speculate
on His Majesty's order.

37:35.200 --> 37:38.200
The Duke of Ding was assassinated
by pirates last night in revenge.

37:38.280 --> 37:39.680
The Jiying Guards
responsible for escorting him

37:39.760 --> 37:42.160
couldn't save him
and lost their lives too.

37:43.520 --> 37:45.560
The pirates of Dongyu Sea always
use their backhand to attack.

37:46.480 --> 37:47.920
The knife edge will only
go from bottom to top,

37:48.000 --> 37:49.120
wide at the front and narrow at the back.

37:49.200 --> 37:50.880
It's completely different
from the one on the body.

37:51.680 --> 37:54.920
Eunuch Wang, wouldn't you know that?

37:58.240 --> 37:59.840
The pirates are cunning.

37:59.920 --> 38:03.520
Maybe it was intentional.

38:03.600 --> 38:04.800
Eunuch Wang!

38:04.880 --> 38:07.080
The Duke of Ding is dead!
Tell the truth now!

38:08.760 --> 38:09.600
The death of the Duke of Ding

38:09.680 --> 38:11.360
was definitely not the fault
of the Criminal Investigation Service

38:11.440 --> 38:13.520
or His Majesty's instruction.

38:13.600 --> 38:16.400
It happened suddenly.
We haven't reported this to His Majesty.

38:16.480 --> 38:17.720
Please return to your residence
and wait for the decree.

38:17.800 --> 38:19.520
Once the Directorate of Ceremonial
investigates this,

38:19.600 --> 38:21.840
we will know what happened.

38:42.960 --> 38:43.960
Uncle.

38:45.240 --> 38:47.320
Had I returned with you,

38:49.960 --> 38:51.840
this wouldn't have happened.

38:53.320 --> 38:55.360
This wouldn't be the case.

39:38.400 --> 39:40.320
-And you still want me to wait!
-General Song!

39:40.400 --> 39:42.240
Should I wait until my uncle is
falsely accused

39:42.320 --> 39:44.680
or for the decree to execute
my whole family?

39:44.760 --> 39:46.720
General Song, you must not be impulsive…

39:46.800 --> 39:47.680
Get lost!

39:47.760 --> 39:49.080
Yan Tang, what are you doing?

39:49.160 --> 39:51.080
Since His Majesty doesn't know of this,

39:51.160 --> 39:52.640
I'll take Eunuch Wang to report it to him!

39:52.720 --> 39:54.560
-Yan Tang, calm down!
-General Song!

39:54.640 --> 39:56.480
-General Song!
-Get out of the way!

39:56.560 --> 39:57.800
General Song!

40:01.080 --> 40:05.880
THE ORIGIN OF ALL BEGINNINGS

40:09.400 --> 40:14.240
GRAND HIGH MYSTIC HALL

40:17.800 --> 40:19.600
WAN MIN, THE EMPRESS

40:19.680 --> 40:21.880
Wearing the proper clothing

40:23.240 --> 40:24.680
to pray to God.

40:25.280 --> 40:26.800
Solemn

40:26.880 --> 40:28.440
and sincere.

40:28.520 --> 40:31.480
Kneel. Bow.

40:34.000 --> 40:35.840
Natural disasters are everywhere now.

40:36.440 --> 40:38.000
The people are suffering.

40:38.520 --> 40:40.680
This is my crime.

40:41.280 --> 40:43.920
I hope that
the Heavenly Lord will protect us.

40:44.440 --> 40:46.000
Bless my people.

40:46.880 --> 40:48.760
Never do evil.

40:49.560 --> 40:52.320
Be healthy every year.

40:54.160 --> 40:55.520
Yan Tang!

40:55.600 --> 40:57.040
This is a capital crime.
Have you thought about it?

40:57.120 --> 40:59.040
If my life can keep my uncle's name clear

40:59.120 --> 41:00.840
and the many lives in the Jiang family,

41:00.920 --> 41:01.760
it's worth it!

41:07.080 --> 41:08.480
-Back off! Don't come over!
-Get out of the way!

41:08.560 --> 41:09.640
I want to see His Majesty!

41:12.640 --> 41:13.840
-Get out of the way!
-Song Mo?

41:13.920 --> 41:14.920
He's one of us.

41:15.000 --> 41:16.160
He's one of us.

41:16.240 --> 41:18.400
Gu Yu, he is looking for death.

41:18.480 --> 41:20.000
Why not stop him
since you know it's a capital crime?

41:20.760 --> 41:22.320
Aunt Min, this is an emergency.

41:22.400 --> 41:23.440
Get out of the way!

41:33.560 --> 41:35.600
If Your Majesty suspects the officer,
you will punish him.

41:35.680 --> 41:37.800
If Your Majesty wanted
the Duke of Ding dead,

41:37.880 --> 41:39.200
you could have offered him poisoned wine.

41:40.160 --> 41:42.280
When an officer dies,
he will keep his dignity.

41:42.360 --> 41:45.000
Why must Your Majesty
torture him all the way?

41:45.640 --> 41:46.880
Even when he is dead,

41:47.400 --> 41:49.920
Your Majesty used
the pirates' revenge as an excuse

41:50.000 --> 41:52.720
to humiliate someone who
fought pirates for half his life!

41:54.080 --> 41:55.240
I boldly ask Your Majesty

41:55.320 --> 41:57.400
to make this clear.

41:57.480 --> 41:58.640
I will never regret it.

42:02.000 --> 42:03.560
No matter how serious the matter is,

42:03.640 --> 42:05.360
there is no reason for you to do this.

42:07.520 --> 42:09.240
Who… Who is dead?

42:09.760 --> 42:10.840
Your Majesty.

42:10.920 --> 42:12.760
Jiang Mei Sun, the Duke of Ding,

42:12.840 --> 42:14.480
died unjustly in the boat's cabin
on the way back to the capital.

42:17.720 --> 42:18.760
How could that happen?

42:20.040 --> 42:22.760
I… I am still waiting for him.

42:23.280 --> 42:25.120
I'm still waiting for him
to return and ask me questions!

42:27.520 --> 42:28.680
Who is it?

42:30.200 --> 42:31.880
Who was so bold to harm him?

42:31.960 --> 42:33.600
Who is it?

42:33.680 --> 42:34.680
Your Majesty…

42:38.920 --> 42:40.280
This is my uncle's.

42:41.360 --> 42:43.080
It's also a token
between Your Majesty and him.

42:44.080 --> 42:45.200
He held it

42:46.880 --> 42:48.480
in his hand until he died.

42:49.880 --> 42:51.240
If there's truth behind this,

42:52.120 --> 42:53.400
Your Majesty, please investigate it!

43:13.040 --> 43:14.000
We're allies.

43:14.080 --> 43:16.520
But General Yan,
you actually threatened me.

43:16.600 --> 43:17.920
That's a different story then.

43:18.000 --> 43:19.640
Your Majesty!

43:19.720 --> 43:22.560
Arrest this treacherous
and unscrupulous man!

43:22.640 --> 43:25.800
You're committing a capital crime.

43:25.880 --> 43:27.200
If we don't get rid of the roots,

43:27.280 --> 43:29.560
we'll be in big trouble.

45:18.480 --> 45:20.800
MEDICAL ACTS AND DRUGS IN THIS DRAMA
ARE FICTIONAL. DO NOT IMITATE.
